This article is a transcript of a press gaggle held by Press Secretary Robert Gibbs aboard Air Force One. The press asked questions about the President's trip to New Orleans and the ongoing situation in the Gulf, as well as the recent incident in Times Square. Gibbs provided updates on the President's schedule, discussed the efforts to cap the oil well, and mentioned discussions with BP executives. He also mentioned that the President had been briefed on the situation in New York and that the investigation was ongoing.